Cosmotron is a programming-free Java web service and web application
framework for relational databases.  With Cosmotron, the database IS the
application. 

BUILDING
========

1. Run the configure script to probe your system and generate the
Makefiles. 

        ./configure

2. Compile using Make.

   	make

3. Install using Make.

        sudo make install

4. Run Cosmotron using Make.

        cosmotron
